{"lastModified":1775736311826,"value":{"kind":"APP_PAGE","html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"ja\" class=\"geist_a71539c9-module__T19VSG__variable h-full antialiased\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.16t1db8_9y2o~.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0ntmlk~gwblc8.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0ze4gu236oq96.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0bzh1n34o8-yk.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0bogtdbh.dcu1.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14.rr0ukvgjw1.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0pqt~8bl3ukh4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-0v3uxu8erarcl.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0c1olp-dk4axa.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/12-mh6_2x1bnb.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>LeadFlow - リード管理ツール</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"インサイドセールス向けシンプルリード管理ツール\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen bg-white\"><nav class=\"fixed top-0 w-full bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md z-50 border-b border-gray-100\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target w-4 h-4 text-white\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><span class=\"font-bold text-lg\">LeadFlow</span></div><a href=\"#signup\" class=\"bg-blue-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm font-medium hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors\">無料で始める</a></div></nav><section class=\"pt-32 pb-20 px-4 sm:px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-3.5 h-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg>完全無料で今すぐ使える</div><h1 class=\"text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight mb-6\">スプレッドシートでの<br class=\"hidden sm:block\"/>リード管理、もう限界では？</h1><p class=\"text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed\">LeadFlowは、インサイドセールス現場のために作られた シンプルなリード管理ツール。資料の閲覧トラッキング付きで、 最適なタイミングでアプローチできます。</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\"><a href=\"#signup\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-base font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20\">無料で始める<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a><a class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-gray-100 text-gray-700 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-base font-semibold hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors\" href=\"/\">デモを体験<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg></a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4\">こんな課題、ありませんか？</h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-center mb-12\">インサイドセールスの現場で毎日起きている問題</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-clock w-6 h-6 text-orange-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 6v6l4 2\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">リスト管理に時間がかかりすぎる</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">スプレッドシートの更新や共有が手間。忙しいと誰も見なくなり、重複架電や対応漏れが発生。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-purple-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-eye w-6 h-6 text-purple-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2.062 12.348a1 1 0 0 1 0-.696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1 19.876 0 1 1 0 0 1 0 .696 10.75 10.75 0 0 1-19.876 0\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"3\"></circle></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">資料を送った後が見えない</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">「資料送りました」の後、見てるのか見てないのかわからない。フォローのタイミングを逃す。</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column w-6 h-6 text-blue-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2\">活動の成果が可視化できない</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">架電数やアポ率を手動で集計。どの行動が商談に繋がったか分析できず、改善が進まない。</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-4 sm:px-6\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4\">LeadFlowでできること</h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-center mb-12\">必要な機能だけ。シンプルだから、現場で使われる。</p><div class=\"space-y-16\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-600 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target w-3 h-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg>リード管理</div><h3 class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">リードの状態が一目でわかる</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">新規→アプローチ中→アポ獲得まで、ワンクリックでステータス更新。「今日誰に連絡すべきか」が自動で表示されます。CSVインポートでスプレッドシートからの移行も簡単。</p></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full\"><div class=\"bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 flex items-center justify-center min-h-48\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target w-20 h-20 text-gray-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse gap-8 items-center\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text w-3 h-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg>資料トラッキング</div><h3 class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">「いつ・何秒見たか」がわかる</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">PDFや外部URLにトラッキングURLを発行。リードが資料を開くと、閲覧日時・滞在時間を自動記録。資料を見た直後の「ホットな瞬間」にアプローチできます。</p></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full\"><div class=\"bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 flex items-center justify-center min-h-48\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-file-text w-20 h-20 text-gray-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M6 22a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h8a2.4 2.4 0 0 1 1.704.706l3.588 3.588A2.4 2.4 0 0 1 20 8v12a2 2 0 0 1-2 2z\"></path><path d=\"M14 2v5a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h5\"></path><path d=\"M10 9H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 13H8\"></path><path d=\"M16 17H8\"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center\"><div class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-600 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column w-3 h-3\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg>ダッシュボード</div><h3 class=\"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">チームの活動を即座に把握</h3><p class=\"text-gray-500 leading-relaxed\">パイプラインの状況、今日のタスク、商談化率、最近の閲覧状況をリアルタイムで可視化。日報作成の手間もゼロに。</p></div><div class=\"flex-1 w-full\"><div class=\"bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 flex items-center justify-center min-h-48\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chart-column w-20 h-20 text-gray-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16\"></path><path d=\"M18 17V9\"></path><path d=\"M13 17V5\"></path><path d=\"M8 17v-3\"></path></svg></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 bg-gray-50\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-4\">他のツールとの違い</h2><p class=\"text-gray-500 text-center mb-12\">「ちょうどいい」を目指しました</p><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b\"><th class=\"text-left p-4 font-medium text-gray-500 w-40\"></th><th class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-400\">スプレッドシート</th><th class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-400\">Salesforce等</th><th class=\"p-4 font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-50/50\">LeadFlow</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-b last:border-0\"><td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-700\">月額費用</td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><span class=\"\">無料</span></td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><span class=\"\">¥3,000〜/人</span></td><td class=\"p-4 text-center bg-blue-50/50 font-medium\"><span class=\"text-blue-600 font-bold\">無料</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b last:border-0\"><td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-700\">導入の手軽さ</td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><span class=\"text-green-600\">簡単</span></td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><span class=\"text-red-500\">複雑</span></td><td class=\"p-4 text-center bg-blue-50/50 font-medium\"><span class=\"text-green-600\">簡単</span></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b last:border-0\"><td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-700\">リード管理</td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><span class=\"text-yellow-600\">△</span></td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mx-auto\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></td><td class=\"p-4 text-center bg-blue-50/50 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mx-auto\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b last:border-0\"><td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-700\">資料トラッキング</td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></td><td class=\"p-4 text-center bg-blue-50/50 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mx-auto\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg></td></tr><tr class=\"border-b last:border-0\"><td class=\"p-4 font-medium text-gray-700\">閲覧通知</td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 6 6 18\"></path><path d=\"m6 6 12 12\"></path></svg></td><td class=\"p-4 text-center \"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-x w-5 h-5 text-gray-300 mx-auto\" aria-hidden=\"true\">